&lt;li&gt;Derek Erskine in the 1925 silent film &lt;i&gt;The Scarlet Woman: An Ecclesiastical Melodrama&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Carleton Hobbs in the 1965 film &lt;i&gt;A King's Story&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Michael Osborne in the 1975 ATV drama series &lt;i&gt;Edward the Seventh&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Marius Goring in the 1978 Thames Television series &lt;i&gt;Edward &amp;amp; Mrs. Simpson&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
